<br>
2.  The main contributor to the cheapening of the EQ experience is all the crazy melee equipment out there which can give a melee to do melee and spell damage.  VI should either take many of those items out of the game, which of course they wont, or give us some half decent  equipment that isn't +whatever intelligence.  Show some creativity in design and throw us a bone here with some decent equipment.<br>
<br>
3.  As said before, remove the hard 6 level cap - enough said<br>
<br>
4.  Finally, VI should stop giving mobs more and more hps with meaner and meaner aes and come up with some creative mobs.  Perhaps some mobs that can't be hit with melee.  perhaps some mobs that can only be hit with a certain line of spells.  The possibilities are endless.<br>
<br>
